12:40.093 --> 12:43.396 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: So, is this
policy effective?

12:43.496 --> 12:45.298 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Does it make U.S. citizens
