12:45.398 --> 12:48.101 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
For one perspective, I am joined
now by Michael
Leiter.

12:48.201 --> 12:54.607 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
He was the director of the
National Counterterrorism
Center from 2007 to 2011, during
both the

12:54.707 --> 12:57.944 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
