administrations.

12:58.044 --> 12:59.812 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Michael Leiter, welcome back to
the program.

12:59.912 --> 13:04.017 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
What's your general reaction to
what Sean
Spicer is saying is the White
House rationale

13:04.117 --> 13:05.718 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
for this?

13:05.818 --> 13:07.553 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MICHAEL LEITER, Former Director,
National
Counterterrorism Center: Well, I
think, as

13:07.654 --> 13:10.723 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
