comes from.

13:39.252 --> 13:43.589 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
So, based on all of those
things, I really
don't see this right now as
being an effective

13:43.690 --> 13:45.324 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
