13:45.425 --> 13:47.827 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: So, you're
referring, among
other things, to the fact that a
number of

13:47.927 --> 13:52.565 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
