16:05.531 --> 16:09.769 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MICHAEL LEITER: I think the
answer on these
countries is, I don't see it.

16:09.869 --> 16:14.507 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And we have to remember the ways
