making it more -- stricter?

16:54.747 --> 16:58.751 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MICHAEL LEITER: Well, it's hard
to figure
out, quite honestly, Judy.

16:58.851 --> 17:01.721 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
