before they
even get that visa.

17:25.945 --> 17:29.315 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And then they undergo additional
screening
while they're traveling.

17:29.415 --> 17:31.350 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
