you're most concerned
with becoming terrorists.

17:48.668 --> 17:51.337 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
In the case of Syrian refugees,
that's less
than 2 percent of the
population.

17:51.437 --> 17:56.509 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: One other
