28:40.719 --> 28:43.922 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MARCIA COYLE, "The National Law
Journal":
Well, I think the original list
really did

28:44.022 --> 28:50.762 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
