separate these two, if that's
who they are,

29:59.197 --> 30:02.534 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
the finalists, from that long
list that we
originally saw?

30:02.634 --> 30:04.169 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MICHAEL CARVIN, Former Deputy
Assistant Attorney
General: Well, to echo what
Marcia said, they'd

30:04.269 --> 30:06.071 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
