your own personal
values, to act as an umpire, not
as a legislator.

30:16.682 --> 30:21.953 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I think Judge Gorsuch probably
digs a little
deeper into the law and is more
vocal, if

30:22.054 --> 30:23.955 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
you will, about the virtues of
originalism.

30:24.056 --> 30:25.724 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Deeper than?

30:25.824 --> 30:31.263 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MICHAEL CARVIN: Judge Hardiman,
