30:52.684 --> 30:54.453 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ELIZABETH WYDRA, Constitutional
Accountability
Center: Yes, I think whichever
one is the

30:54.553 --> 30:57.589 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
nominee, we're going to be look
very closely
to see whether he is someone who
will apply

30:57.689 --> 31:02.294 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
