finalists,

31:48.306 --> 31:51.042 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Judge Gorsuch and Judge
Hardiman.

31:51.143 --> 31:52.043 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
What do you see?

31:52.144 --> 31:53.979 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
What are you looking for?

31:54.079 --> 31:55.347 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
TOM GOLDSTEIN, Founder,
SCOTUSblog.com: Well,
I think that the president
really is going

31:55.447 --> 31:57.816 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
