preserving the status
quo of a relatively liberal
court.

34:29.768 --> 34:34.172 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Nonetheless, I think, partially
because of
the Garland issue, the Democrats
are going

34:34.272 --> 34:36.107 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
to make this a lot of sound and
fury.

34:36.207 --> 34:40.011 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: The Garland issue
