40:16.281 --> 40:20.151 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MILES O'BRIEN: More perspective
on these issues
now from Angel Cabrera, the
president of the

40:20.251 --> 40:25.490 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
George Mason University, the
