41:38.496 --> 41:41.833 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MILES O'BRIEN: My understanding
is most student
don't have green cards.

41:41.933 --> 41:42.900 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
