41:43.000 --> 41:44.802 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
ANGEL CABRERA: That's correct.

41:44.902 --> 41:47.872 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MILES O'BRIEN: Which means that
that carve-out
for green cards that we have
been talking

41:47.972 --> 41:51.209 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
about the past couple of days
