to most of these students.

41:51.309 --> 41:56.581 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, give us an idea of the
immediate impact
on your campus and campuses
elsewhere in the

41:56.681 --> 41:57.582 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
U.S.

41:57.682 --> 41:59.417 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
ANGEL CABRERA: Yes.

41:59.517 --> 42:04.789 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Well, in our case, we have 82
students who
have what we call an F-1 visa,
which is a

42:04.889 --> 42:07.058 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
student visa, from those
countries.

42:07.158 --> 42:12.897 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
