to us.

42:31.749 --> 42:35.820 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
So she may have to cancel
classes this semester
and try to figure out whether
maybe she can

42:35.920 --> 42:37.488 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
take some of the class online.

42:37.588 --> 42:40.958 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MILES O'BRIEN: What is your
advice to students
whether they're here or there?

42:41.058 --> 42:48.366 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ANGEL CABRERA: Well, what we're
telling our
employees, our students, our
faculty is, don't

42:48.466 --> 42:55.039 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
