it's more clear,
because if you step outside of
the United

42:55.139 --> 42:57.608 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
States, you may not be able to
come back in.

42:57.708 --> 42:59.844 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
