than done.

42:59.944 --> 43:05.016 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Some of them have research
projects or they
may have even family issues that
require for

43:05.116 --> 43:06.684 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
