subsequently killed.

43:25.903 --> 43:31.309 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Is there a sense among yourself
and other
college presidents that this is
a measure

43:31.409 --> 43:33.344 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
