evidence.

43:51.028 --> 43:55.433 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
On our campus, our students from
those countries
actually have never posed a
threat of any

43:55.533 --> 43:57.335 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
kind.

43:57.435 --> 44:00.638 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
On the contrary, I think that
the presence
of people from all over the
world increases

44:00.738 --> 44:02.673 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
