44:08.212 --> 44:11.649 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
You start to understand how
things are perceived
from other angles.

44:11.749 --> 44:19.123 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, from my perspective, one of
the best things
that one can do to in fact
improve the understanding

44:19.223 --> 44:24.762 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
and diminish the probability of
safety issues
is to create understanding, is
to engage in

44:24.862 --> 44:26.597 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
scholarly exchange.

44:26.697 --> 44:30.501 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
MILES O'BRIEN: It's worth
putting this, I
think, in context into the
larger economic

44:30.601 --> 44:32.203 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
