would this
have, ultimately, potentially,
on jobs in

44:48.586 --> 44:50.354 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
America?

44:50.454 --> 44:54.058 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ANGEL CABRERA: Well, I think
when we talk
about immigration, most people
start thinking

44:54.158 --> 44:56.260 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
