labor.

44:56.360 --> 45:02.033 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The part that is left out, and
it shouldn't
because it's essential to the
economy of the

45:02.133 --> 45:05.503 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
