knowledge worker.

45:05.603 --> 45:11.876 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It's the graduate student; 75
percent or more
of graduate students in
engineering and computer

45:11.976 --> 45:15.112 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
