today are immigrants.

45:15.212 --> 45:18.549 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
When you look at start-ups in
technology,
some of the most innovative
companies, the

45:18.649 --> 45:23.521 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
