want to work
for, about 40 percent of those
that have achieved

45:23.621 --> 45:27.358 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
$1 billion or more were founded
or co-founded
by immigrants.

45:27.458 --> 45:32.997 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
If you look at scientific
achievement, 40
percent of the Nobel Prize
winners in this

45:33.097 --> 45:39.070 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
